				<p class="intro">The Department of Biochemistry and Molecular Genetics is one of five Basic Science Departments in the College of Medicine at UIC.</p>
				<p>"During the last several decades there have been a series of dramatic advances in the way basic biomedical research is carried out. We are now able to produce large quantities of single proteins and determine their structures at atomic resolution, we can mutate these proteins and modify their properties... [ <a href="aboutus/index.html" class="readmore">READ MORE +</a> ]</p>
		  <!-- InstanceEndEditable --></div>
			
